for understanding how
cancer cells process energy

00:34:03.630 --> 00:34:06.370
in different ways
than normal cells

00:34:06.370 --> 00:34:08.320
and whether we can
figure out a better

00:34:08.320 --> 00:34:11.260
way to target cancer
cells by understanding

00:34:11.260 --> 00:34:12.560
those differences.

